the midship compass. That was about the mid- 
dle of the boat. Well, when you are sharp-set, 
and you eat and satisfy yourself, everything 
looks pretty different from what it done before. 
It makes a body feel pretty near comfortable, 
even when he is up in a balloon with a genius. 
We got to talking together. 

There was one thing that kept bothering me, 
and by and by I says : 

"Tom., did n't we start east ?" 

"Yes." 

" How fast have we been oroinor ?" 

" Well, you heard what the professor said when 
