really gone and they could n't get us, they sat 
down on their hams and looked up at us so kind 
of disappointed that it was as much as a person 
could do not to see their side of the matter. 



CHAPTER VI. 

IT S A CARAVAN. 

I WAS SO weak that the only thing I wanted was 
