and making me do this, and making me do that 
and t'other, and always selecting out the things 
I did n't want to do, and then giving me Sam 
Hill because I shirked and done something else, 
and just aggravating the life out of a body all 
the time ; but up here in the sky it was so still 
and sunshiny and lovely, and plenty to eat, and 



TOM RESPECTS THE FLEA. 109 

plenty of sleep, and strange things to see, and 
